    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition, and the price reflects exactly that \u2014 please read the full description so you understand what you're getting. This is a genuinely exceptional example that stands out even among well-maintained used cars. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint retains a deep, uniform gloss with no visible scratches, chips, swirl marks, or fading. Every panel is straight, the trim is intact and properly fitted, and the glass is clear and free of chips or cracks. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 the seats, carpets, headliner, and dashboard all look and feel virtually new, with no tears, stains, or excessive wear anywhere. All electronics, controls, and comfort features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, starts immediately, and runs with a smooth, confident idle. The drivetrain performs flawlessly with no hesitation, unusual noises, or warning lights. Mechanically, this car has been well cared for and shows it in every way. Maintenance is current, and there are no known issues to disclose. If you're looking for a used vehicle that genuinely feels like new, this is a rare opportunity \u2014 and the price reflects that honestly.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want any potential buyer to have a fully realistic picture before reaching out. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable scratches, dents, and areas where the paint has faded, chipped, or peeled. The body may have rust or corrosion in spots that will require attention. The interior is similarly worn, with damaged upholstery, cracked or broken trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require meaningful repairs to bring it to reliable daily-driver status \u2014 it is not in turn-key condition. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or seeking parts. We are pricing it accordingly to reflect its true state, and we encourage serious buyers to inspect the vehicle in person before purchasing.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great opportunity to get behind the wheel of a reliable, well-cared-for vehicle! This car is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, has been properly maintained, and is ready to take on daily driving with confidence. You'll notice it has been looked after thoughtfully, with only the minor signs of normal use you'd expect from a car that's actually been enjoyed. If you're looking for a dependable ride that delivers real value without the mint-condition price tag, this one deserves a closer look!",
      "price": 34500.0,
