      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we want to give you a complete and honest picture of what that means. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains a healthy shine with only minor surface scratches and a couple of small door dings that are typical of a well-used vehicle. There is no significant rust or body damage to report. The interior is clean and functional; the upholstery shows normal wear consistent with regular use, including some light scuffing on the driver's seat and minor fading on the dashboard trim, but nothing that detracts significantly from comfort or appearance. All major interior controls and features are in working order. Mechanically, this car has been maintained and runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, the transmission shifts without hesitation, and the brakes respond well. Tires have adequate tread remaining for continued use, though you may want to plan for replacement within the next year or so depending on your driving habits. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that has been honestly cared for. It won't dazzle you like a showroom model, but it will serve you well as a reliable everyday driver at a fair price.",
      "price": 33500.0,
